      <section id=3D"references">
        <!-- review? -->
        <h3><span>3.5 </span>References</h3>
        <p>
          The References section requires specific <a href=3D"https://w3c.g=
ithub.io/scholarly-html/#citations">semantic overlays</a>
          (reference) as well as strict content structure. Apart from a (re=
quired) <code>hx</code>
          element, it must contain only one <code>ol</code> or <code>dl</co=
de> element.
        </p>
